  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\nI wrote a lot of characters in Message Box and send message. But, old characters were not erased when I wrote again.\r\n\r\nVideo: [https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GMceq-2Iuin9VwxldaATMNGDLY19EoST/view](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GMceq-2Iuin9VwxldaATMNGDLY19EoST/view)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Sign in\r\n- Chat with console\r\n- Click Message Box\r\n- Write characters\r\n- Send message\r\n- Click Message Box\r\n- Write characters\r\n- Send message\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\n- Older characters should be deleted after sending a message.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: 0.9.12+\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android 6.0 - LG G4 (Real Device)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
